{"id": "figure_019", "modality": "figures", "name": "Faster R-CNN (RPN + RoI head)", "task": {"description": "Create a single 1920x1080 self-contained HTML file using ONLY inline CSS and inline SVG reproducing the Faster R-CNN architecture. Title 'Faster R-CNN (Ren et al., 2015)'. Flow: input image -> CNN backbone (conv feature map) -> Region Proposal Network (RPN) with a sliding-window 3x3 conv, k anchor boxes, and two sibling 1x1 convs (cls: 2k scores, reg: 4k coords) -> proposals -> RoI Pooling (using both the feature map and proposals) -> two FC layers -> two sibling heads (softmax classifier, bbox regressor). Show the anchor-box inset (k=9, 3 scales x 3 ratios).", "requirements": ["The flow image -> backbone -> RPN -> RoI Pooling -> FC -> heads is left-to-right and connected by arrows", "The RPN shows a 3x3 sliding window and two sibling 1x1 conv branches labeled cls (2k) and reg (4k)", "RoI Pooling takes inputs from BOTH the backbone feature map and the RPN proposals (two incoming arrows)", "Two sibling output heads (classifier softmax, bbox regressor) are shown after the FC layers", "An inset shows k=9 anchors as 3 scales x 3 aspect ratios", "The two sibling 1x1 conv branches (and the two output heads) are equal-size and aligned pairs", "No element overlaps; arrows do not cross unrelated block labels", "The anchor inset does not overlap the main flow", "The whole figure fits in 1920x1080 with no scrollbar", "A legend maps colors/arrow styles; blocks have shape annotations; nothing clipped or misaligned"]}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 4928, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 2, "rv_total_tokens": 18140}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 1, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 5816, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 6151}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 5400, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 28890}], "ss_img": "images/figures/figure_019_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/figures/figure_019_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Faster R-CNN Architecture</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);\n            width: 1880px;\n            height: 1040px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        \n        .title {\n            font-size: 48px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"title\">Faster R-CNN (Ren et al., 2015)</div>\n        \n        <svg width=\"1880\" height=\"900\" viewBox=\"0 0 1880 900\">\n            <!-- Background -->\n            <defs>\n                <linearGradient id=\"bgGrad\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#ffffff;stop-opacity:0.8\" />\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#f8f9fa;stop-opacity:0.8\" />\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <filter id=\"shadow\" x=\"-20%\" y=\"-20%\" width=\"140%\" height=\"140%\">\n                    <feDropShadow dx=\"3\" dy=\"3\" stdDeviation=\"3\" flood-color=\"#000000\" flood-opacity=\"0.2\"/>\n                </filter>\n                \n                <pattern id=\"convPattern\" patternUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\">\n                    <rect width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#3498db\"/>\n                    <rect width=\"4\" height=\"4\" fill=\"#2980b9\"/>\n                </pattern>\n            </defs>\n            \n            <!-- Main flow arrows -->\n            <defs>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" \n                        refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#34495e\" />\n                </marker>\n            </defs>\n            \n            <!-- Input Image -->\n            <rect x=\"50\" y=\"200\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" filter=\"url(#shadow)\"/>\n            <text x=\"110\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">Input</text>\n            <text x=\"110\" y=\"270\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">Image</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow 1 -->\n            <line x1=\"180\" y1=\"260\" x2=\"230\" y2=\"260\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- CNN Backbone -->\n            <rect x=\"250\" y=\"180\" width=\"160\" height=\"160\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"url(#convPattern)\" filter=\"url(#shadow)\"/>\n            <text x=\"330\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\">CNN</text>\n            <text x=\"330\" y=\"260\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\">Backbone</text>\n            <text x=\"330\" y=\"285\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">(Conv Feature Map)</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow 2 -->\n            <line x1=\"420\" y1=\"260\" x2=\"470\" y2=\"260\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Region Proposal Network (RPN) -->\n            <rect x=\"490\" y=\"120\" width=\"280\" height=\"280\" rx=\"12\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" filter=\"url(#shadow)\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"630\" y=\"145\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\">Region Proposal Network (RPN)</text>\n            \n            <!-- Sliding window 3x3 conv -->\n            <rect x=\"510\" y=\"160\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\" filter=\"url(#shadow)\"/>\n            <text x=\"560\" y=\"185\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">3\u00d73 Conv</text>\n            <text x=\"560\" y=\"200\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">(sliding window)</text>\n            \n            <!-- K anchor boxes visualization -->\n            <rect x=\"630\" y=\"160\" width=\"120\" height=\"60\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#e67e22\" filter=\"url(#shadow)\"/>\n            <text x=\"690\" y=\"185\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">k Anchor Boxes</text>\n            <text x=\"690\" y=\"200\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">(k=9)</text>\n            \n            <!-- Two sibling 1x1 convs -->\n            <rect x=\"510\" y=\"240\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#27ae60\" filter=\"url(#shadow)\"/>\n            <text x=\"560\" y=\"260\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">1\u00d71 Conv</text>\n            <text x=\"560\" y=\"275\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\">cls: 2k scores</text>\n            <text x=\"560\" y=\"290\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\">(obj/bg)</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"630\" y=\"240\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#f39c12\" filter=\"url(#shadow)\"/>\n            <text x=\"680\" y=\"260\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">1\u00d71 Conv</text>\n            <text x=\"680\" y=\"275\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\">reg: 4k coords</text>\n            <text x=\"680\" y=\"290\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\">(bbox)</text>\n            \n            <!-- Anchor box detail inset -->\n            <rect x=\"510\" y=\"320\" width=\"240\" height=\"70\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"630\" y=\"340\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Anchor Box Details (k=9)</text>\n            <text x=\"630\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"11\">3 scales \u00d7 3 aspect ratios</text>\n            <text x=\"630\" y=\"370\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"11\">Scales: 128\u00b2, 256\u00b2, 512\u00b2 | Ratios: 1:1, 1:2, 2:1</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow 3 -->\n            <line x1=\"780\" y1=\"260\" x2=\"830\" y2=\"260\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"805\" y=\"245\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Proposals</text>\n            \n            <!-- RoI Pooling -->\n            <rect x=\"850\" y=\"200\" width=\"140\" height=\"120\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#16a085\" filter=\"url(#shadow)\"/>\n            <text x=\"920\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">RoI Pooling</text>\n            <text x=\"920\" y=\"260\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">(Feature Map +</text>\n            <text x=\"920\" y=\"275\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">Proposals)</text>\n            \n            <!-- Connection from CNN backbone to RoI Pooling -->\n            <path d=\"M 330 340 Q 330 380 590 380 Q 850 380 920 320\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"625\" y=\"395\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"11\">Feature Map</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow 4 -->\n            <line x1=\"1000\" y1=\"260\" x2=\"1050\" y2=\"260\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- FC Layers -->\n            <rect x=\"1070\" y=\"200\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" filter=\"url(#shadow)\"/>\n            <text x=\"1130\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">FC Layers</text>\n            <text x=\"1130\" y=\"260\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">(4096 \u2192 4096)</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow 5 -->\n            <line x1=\"1200\" y1=\"260\" x2=\"1250\" y2=\"260\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Final Classification and Regression Heads -->\n            <rect x=\"1270\" y=\"150\" width=\"140\" height=\"80\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" filter=\"url(#shadow)\"/>\n            <text x=\"1340\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">Softmax</text>\n            <text x=\"1340\" y=\"200\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">Classifier</text>\n            <text x=\"1340\" y=\"215\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\">(C+1 classes)</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1270\" y=\"250\" width=\"140\" height=\"80\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#f39c12\" filter=\"url(#shadow)\"/>\n            <text x=\"1340\" y=\"280\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">Bbox</text>\n            <text x=\"1340\" y=\"300\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">Regressor</text>\n            <text x=\"1340\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\">(4\u00d7C coords)</text>\n            \n            <!-- Branching arrows to final heads -->\n            <line x1=\"1250\" y1=\"260\" x2=\"1270\" y2=\"190\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"1250\" y1=\"260\" x2=\"1270\" y2=\"290\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Final outputs -->\n            <rect x=\"1450\" y=\"150\" width=\"120\" height=\"60\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#2ecc71\" filter=\"url(#shadow)\"/>\n            <text x=\"1510\" y=\"175\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Class Scores</text>\n            <text x=\"1510\" y=\"190\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">&amp; Probabilities</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1450\" y=\"270\" width=\"120\" height=\"60\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#f1c40f\" filter=\"url(#shadow)\"/>\n            <text x=\"1510\" y=\"295\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Refined</text>\n            <text x=\"1510\" y=\"310\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">Bounding Boxes</text>\n            \n            <!-- Final arrows -->\n            <line x1=\"1420\" y1=\"190\" x2=\"1440\" y2=\"180\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <line x1=\"1420\" y1=\"290\" x2=\"1440\" y2=\"300\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Stage labels -->\n            <text x=\"110\" y=\"380\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">Stage 1:</text>\n            <text x=\"110\" y=\"400\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Feature</text>\n            <text x=\"110\" y=\"415\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Extraction</text>\n            \n            <text x=\"630\" y=\"450\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">Stage 2: Region Proposal</text>\n            \n            <text x=\"1340\" y=\"380\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">Stage 3:</text>\n            <text x=\"1340\" y=\"400\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Classification &amp;</text>\n            <text x=\"1340\" y=\"415\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Regression</text>\n            \n            <!-- Key innovation callout -->\n            <rect x=\"50\" y=\"500\" width=\"300\" height=\"120\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#34495e\" filter=\"url(#shadow)\"/>\n            <text x=\"200\" y=\"525\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\">Key Innovation</text>\n            <text x=\"200\" y=\"550\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" font-size=\"12\">\u2022 End-to-end trainable</text>\n            <text x=\"200\" y=\"570\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" font-size=\"12\">\u2022 Shared conv features</text>\n            <text x=\"200\" y=\"590\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" font-size=\"12\">\u2022 Fast region proposals (~10ms)</text>\n            <text x=\"200\" y=\"610\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" font-size=\"12\">\u2022 State-of-the-art accuracy</text>\n            \n            <!-- Performance metrics -->\n            <rect x=\"400\" y=\"500\" width=\"280\" height=\"120\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#27ae60\" filter=\"url(#shadow)\"/>\n            <text x=\"540\" y=\"525\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\">Performance</text>\n            <text x=\"540\" y=\"550\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">PASCAL VOC 2007: 73.2% mAP</text>\n            <text x=\"540\" y=\"570\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">Speed: ~5 FPS (GPU)</text>\n            <text x=\"540\" y=\"590\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">200\u00d7 faster than R-CNN</text>\n            <text x=\"540\" y=\"610\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">10\u00d7 faster than Fast R-CNN</text>\n            \n        </svg>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Faster R-CNN Architecture</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);\n            overflow: hidden;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n        }\n        \n        .container {\n            width: 1900px;\n            height: 1060px;\n            margin: 10px;\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            padding: 10px;\n        }\n        \n        h1 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 36px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin: 0 0 20px 0;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h1>Faster R-CNN (Ren et al., 2015)</h1>\n        \n        <svg width=\"1880\" height=\"1000\" viewBox=\"0 0 1880 1000\">\n            <!-- Background gradient -->\n            <defs>\n                <linearGradient id=\"bgGrad\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#f8f9fa;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#e9ecef;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <!-- Component gradients -->\n                <linearGradient id=\"inputGrad\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#4CAF50;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#388E3C;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <linearGradient id=\"cnnGrad\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#2196F3;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#1976D2;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <linearGradient id=\"rpnGrad\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#FF9800;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#F57C00;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <linearGradient id=\"roiGrad\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#9C27B0;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#7B1FA2;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <linearGradient id=\"fcGrad\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#E91E63;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#C2185B;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <linearGradient id=\"outputGrad\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#607D8B;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#455A64;stop-opacity:1\" />\n                </linearGradient>\n            </defs>\n            \n            <!-- Background -->\n            <rect width=\"1880\" height=\"1000\" fill=\"url(#bgGrad)\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Input Image -->\n            <rect x=\"50\" y=\"200\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" fill=\"url(#inputGrad)\" rx=\"8\" stroke=\"#2E7D32\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"110\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"600\">Input</text>\n            <text x=\"110\" y=\"270\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"600\">Image</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow 1 -->\n            <path d=\"M 180 260 L 220 260\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- CNN Backbone -->\n            <rect x=\"240\" y=\"150\" width=\"160\" height=\"220\" fill=\"url(#cnnGrad)\" rx=\"8\" stroke=\"#1565C0\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"320\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"700\">CNN Backbone</text>\n            <text x=\"320\" y=\"200\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">(VGG, ResNet)</text>\n            \n            <!-- Feature map representation -->\n            <rect x=\"260\" y=\"220\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" rx=\"4\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"320\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\">Conv Feature</text>\n            <text x=\"320\" y=\"270\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\">Map</text>\n            <text x=\"320\" y=\"290\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\">(H\u00d7W\u00d7D)</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow 2 -->\n            <path d=\"M 410 260 L 450 260\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- RPN Section -->\n            <rect x=\"470\" y=\"80\" width=\"400\" height=\"360\" fill=\"url(#rpnGrad)\" rx=\"8\" stroke=\"#E65100\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"670\" y=\"110\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"700\">Region Proposal Network (RPN)</text>\n            \n            <!-- 3x3 Conv -->\n            <rect x=\"490\" y=\"140\" width=\"100\" height=\"60\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" rx=\"6\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"540\" y=\"165\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\">3\u00d73 Conv</text>\n            <text x=\"540\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\">Sliding Window</text>\n            \n            <!-- Anchor boxes inset -->\n            <rect x=\"620\" y=\"130\" width=\"230\" height=\"120\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.15)\" rx=\"6\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"735\" y=\"150\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"600\">k=9 Anchor Boxes</text>\n            \n            <!-- 3x3 grid of anchor representations -->\n            <g transform=\"translate(650, 160)\">\n                <!-- Scale 1 (small) -->\n                <rect x=\"10\" y=\"10\" width=\"15\" height=\"10\" fill=\"white\" opacity=\"0.8\" rx=\"1\"/>\n                <rect x=\"10\" y=\"30\" width=\"10\" height=\"15\" fill=\"white\" opacity=\"0.8\" rx=\"1\"/>\n                <rect x=\"10\" y=\"55\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"white\" opacity=\"0.8\" rx=\"1\"/>\n                \n                <!-- Scale 2 (medium) -->\n                <rect x=\"70\" y=\"8\" width=\"20\" height=\"14\" fill=\"white\" opacity=\"0.8\" rx=\"1\"/>\n                <rect x=\"70\" y=\"28\" width=\"14\" height=\"20\" fill=\"white\" opacity=\"0.8\" rx=\"1\"/>\n                <rect x=\"70\" y=\"53\" width=\"26\" height=\"10\" fill=\"white\" opacity=\"0.8\" rx=\"1\"/>\n                \n                <!-- Scale 3 (large) -->\n                <rect x=\"140\" y=\"5\" width=\"25\" height=\"18\" fill=\"white\" opacity=\"0.8\" rx=\"1\"/>\n                <rect x=\"140\" y=\"25\" width=\"18\" height=\"25\" fill=\"white\" opacity=\"0.8\" rx=\"1\"/>\n                <rect x=\"140\" y=\"52\" width=\"32\" height=\"12\" fill=\"white\" opacity=\"0.8\" rx=\"1\"/>\n                \n                <!-- Labels -->\n                <text x=\"17\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"9\">Scale 1</text>\n                <text x=\"80\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"9\">Scale 2</text>\n                <text x=\"152\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"9\">Scale 3</text>\n                <text x=\"100\" y=\"95\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">3 Scales \u00d7 3 Ratios</text>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Classification branch -->\n            <rect x=\"490\" y=\"270\" width=\"120\" height=\"60\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" rx=\"6\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"550\" y=\"290\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\">1\u00d71 Conv</text>\n            <text x=\"550\" y=\"305\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\">Classification</text>\n            <text x=\"550\" y=\"320\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">2k scores</text>\n            \n            <!-- Regression branch -->\n            <rect x=\"490\" y=\"350\" width=\"120\" height=\"60\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" rx=\"6\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"550\" y=\"370\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\">1\u00d71 Conv</text>\n            <text x=\"550\" y=\"385\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\">Regression</text>\n            <text x=\"550\" y=\"400\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">4k coords</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrows within RPN -->\n            <path d=\"M 590 170 L 620 170 L 620 300 L 610 300\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowheadWhite)\"/>\n            <path d=\"M 590 170 L 620 170 L 620 380 L 610 380\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowheadWhite)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow 3 - Proposals -->\n            <path d=\"M 880 260 L 920 260\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"900\" y=\"245\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#34495e\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\">Proposals</text>\n            \n            <!-- RoI Pooling -->\n            <rect x=\"940\" y=\"200\" width=\"160\" height=\"120\" fill=\"url(#roiGrad)\" rx=\"8\" stroke=\"#6A1B9A\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"1020\" y=\"230\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"700\">RoI Pooling</text>\n            <text x=\"1020\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">Feature Map +</text>\n            <text x=\"1020\" y=\"270\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">Proposals</text>\n            <text x=\"1020\" y=\"290\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\">\u2192 Fixed Size</text>\n            \n            <!-- Feature map input to RoI -->\n            <path d=\"M 320 370 L 320 450 L 980 450 L 980 320\" stroke=\"#1976D2\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n            <text x=\"650\" y=\"470\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#1976D2\" font-size=\"11\">Feature Map</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow 4 -->\n            <path d=\"M 1110 260 L 1150 260\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- FC Layers -->\n            <rect x=\"1170\" y=\"200\" width=\"140\" height=\"120\" fill=\"url(#fcGrad)\" rx=\"8\" stroke=\"#AD1457\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"1240\" y=\"230\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"700\">FC Layers</text>\n            <rect x=\"1190\" y=\"250\" width=\"100\" height=\"25\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" rx=\"4\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1240\" y=\"267\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"600\">FC 4096</text>\n            <rect x=\"1190\" y=\"280\" width=\"100\" height=\"25\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" rx=\"4\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1240\" y=\"297\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"600\">FC 4096</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow 5 -->\n            <path d=\"M 1320 260 L 1360 260\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Final Classification -->\n            <rect x=\"1380\" y=\"150\" width=\"140\" height=\"80\" fill=\"url(#outputGrad)\" rx=\"8\" stroke=\"#37474F\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"1450\" y=\"175\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"700\">Softmax</text>\n            <text x=\"1450\" y=\"195\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"700\">Classifier</text>\n            <text x=\"1450\" y=\"215\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\">C+1 classes</text>\n            \n            <!-- Final Regression -->\n            <rect x=\"1380\" y=\"270\" width=\"140\" height=\"80\" fill=\"url(#outputGrad)\" rx=\"8\" stroke=\"#37474F\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"1450\" y=\"295\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"700\">Bbox</text>\n            <text x=\"1450\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"700\">Regressor</text>\n            <text x=\"1450\" y=\"335\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\">4\u00d7C coords</text>\n            \n            <!-- Final arrows -->\n            <path d=\"M 1320 240 L 1340 240 L 1340 190 L 1370 190\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <path d=\"M 1320 280 L 1340 280 L 1340 310 L 1370 310\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Output labels -->\n            <text x=\"1600\" y=\"190\" text-anchor=\"start\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"600\">Object Classes</text>\n            <text x=\"1600\" y=\"310\" text-anchor=\"start\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"600\">Bounding Boxes</text>\n            \n            <!-- Legend/Key Information -->\n            <rect x=\"50\" y=\"500\" width=\"800\" height=\"160\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.9)\" rx=\"8\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"70\" y=\"530\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"700\">Key Components:</text>\n            \n            <text x=\"70\" y=\"555\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\">\u2022 CNN Backbone:</text>\n            <text x=\"200\" y=\"555\" fill=\"#34495e\" font-size=\"12\">Extracts feature maps from input image (VGG-16, ResNet, etc.)</text>\n            \n            <text x=\"70\" y=\"575\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\">\u2022 RPN:</text>\n            <text x=\"200\" y=\"575\" fill=\"#34495e\" font-size=\"12\">Generates object proposals using sliding window + anchor boxes</text>\n            \n            <text x=\"70\" y=\"595\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\">\u2022 Anchor Boxes:</text>\n            <text x=\"200\" y=\"595\" fill=\"#34495e\" font-size=\"12\">k=9 boxes per location (3 scales \u00d7 3 aspect ratios: 1:1, 1:2, 2:1)</text>\n            \n            <text x=\"70\" y=\"615\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\">\u2022 RoI Pooling:</text>\n            <text x=\"200\" y=\"615\" fill=\"#34495e\" font-size=\"12\">Extracts fixed-size features from variable-size proposals</text>\n            \n            <text x=\"70\" y=\"635\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\">\u2022 Two-stage Detection:</text>\n            <text x=\"70\" y=\"650\" fill=\"#34495e\" font-size=\"12\">Stage 1: RPN generates proposals, Stage 2: Classification + refinement</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow markers -->\n            <defs>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#34495e\"/>\n                </marker>\n                <marker id=\"arrowheadWhite\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"white\"/>\n                </marker>\n            </defs>\n            \n            <!-- Training info -->\n            <rect x=\"900\" y=\"500\" width=\"400\" height=\"120\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.9)\" rx=\"8\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"920\" y=\"530\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"700\">Training:</text>\n            <text x=\"920\" y=\"555\" fill=\"#34495e\" font-size=\"12\">\u2022 Multi-task loss: RPN classification + regression</text>\n            <text x=\"920\" y=\"575\" fill=\"#34495e\" font-size=\"12\">\u2022 Final classification + bbox regression</text>\n            <text x=\"920\" y=\"595\" fill=\"#34495e\" font-size=\"12\">\u2022 End-to-end training with shared CNN features</text>\n            \n            <!-- Performance info -->\n            <rect x=\"1350\" y=\"500\" width=\"400\" height=\"120\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.9)\" rx=\"8\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1370\" y=\"530\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"700\">Advantages:</text>\n            <text x=\"1370\" y=\"555\" fill=\"#34495e\" font-size=\"12\">\u2022 Faster than R-CNN (shared conv features)</text>\n            <text x=\"1370\" y=\"575\" fill=\"#34495e\" font-size=\"12\">\u2022 Higher accuracy than Fast R-CNN</text>\n            <text x=\"1370\" y=\"595\" fill=\"#34495e\" font-size=\"12\">\u2022 Real-time object detection capability</text>\n        </svg>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}